events concerning women--

00:01:12.970 --> 00:01:14.940
women's history.

00:01:14.940 --> 00:01:17.060
But before we start
today's program

00:01:17.060 --> 00:01:18.360
and introduce our speaker,

00:01:18.360 --> 00:01:21.230
I'd like to give you
just a brief overview

00:01:21.230 --> 00:01:23.630
of our division and
the resources.

00:01:23.630 --> 00:01:26.110
And I've got an agenda today.

00:01:26.110 --> 00:01:31.520
All of my Turkish-speaking and
reading people that have come

00:01:31.520 --> 00:01:34.830
to this program today, I
want to invite you in here

00:01:34.830 --> 00:01:39.320
to use these collections,
read the latest novels.

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:42.640
When you go to travel
