00:02:16.090 --> 00:02:19.150
architecturally about
the buildings.

00:02:19.150 --> 00:02:21.460
There is everything
about archeology,

00:02:21.460 --> 00:02:23.680
how about romance novels?

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:25.410
Come on and read
the latest ones.

