00:03:01.810 --> 00:03:04.810
So, what you can do is
look at the modern Turkish

00:03:04.810 --> 00:03:06.950
and then figure it
out on the other side.

00:03:06.950 --> 00:03:09.240
I love this side by side thing.

00:03:09.240 --> 00:03:12.690
And I'd love to have you
come in and use these works,

00:03:12.690 --> 00:03:15.010
and all you need to do
is search in our catalog.

00:03:15.010 --> 00:03:18.490
You can get a reader
card on the first floor

00:03:18.490 --> 00:03:21.260
and you can even request
the books ahead of time.

00:03:21.260 --> 00:03:22.560
So, they're waiting for you

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:25.170
in our reading room
when you come in.

00:03:25.170 --> 00:03:27.780
And I hope you'll do that.

00:03:27.780 --> 00:03:32.180
Other things, we are
a custodial division

00:03:32.180 --> 00:03:35.620
and we have three sections
that serve the countries

00:03:35.620 --> 00:03:38.820
and collections for
researchers around the world.

